de.oaam.model.oaam.systems

Interface RotaryPower

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ElementA, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ModeDependentElementA, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Power, ProvidedOutputA, RequiredInputA, VariantDependentElementA
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RotaryPowerImpl

    public interface RotaryPower
extends Power
    A representation of the model object 'Rotary Power'. This output or input represents rotary mechanical power

    The following features are supported:

    • Momentum
    • Angular Velocity
    See Also:
    SystemsPackage.getRotaryPower()
